title: Chicago Fire
description: Follows both the professional and personal lives of the firefighters, rescue personnel, and paramedics of the Chicago Fire Department at the fictional Firehouse 51 as they risk their lives to save and protect the city of Chicago, Illinois.

title: Arrow
description: Spoiled billionaire playboy Oliver Queen is missing and presumed dead when his yacht is lost at sea. He returns five years later a changed man, determined to clean up the city as a hooded vigilante armed with a bow.

title: JoJo's Bizarre Adventure
description: The story of the Joestar family, who are possessed with intense psychic strength, and the adventures each member encounters throughout their lives.

title: Major Crimes
description: The Closer (2005) spin-off series, which follows Captain Raydor of the Los Angeles Police Department.

title: Revolution
description: Fifteen years after a permanent global blackout, a group of revolutionaries seek to drive out a tyrannical militia that's taken over the former United States of America.

title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
description: Four ninja turtles, mutated by a mysterious alien substance, must rise up out of the sewers and defend New York City against evil forces from both the past and present.

title: Star vs. the Forces of Evil
description: Star Butterfly arrives on Earth to live with the Diazes, a Mexican-American family. She continues to battle villains throughout the universe and high school, mainly to protect her extremely powerful wand, an object that still confuses her.

title: DreamWorks Dragons
description: The further adventures of Hiccup and his friends on the Island of Berk.

title: Psycho-Pass
description: Believing in humanity and order, policewoman Akane Tsunemori obeys the ruling, computerized, precognitive Sibyl System. But when she faces a criminal mastermind who can elude this perfect system, she questions both Sibyl and herself.

title: Avengers Assemble
description: The further adventures of the Marvel Universe's mightiest general membership superhero team.

title: Ben 10: Omniverse
description: The continuing adventures of Ben Tennyson (Yuri Lowenthal) and his new partner, Rook Blonko (Bumper Robinson).

title: Last Resort
description: A U.S. sub picks up Navy SEALs and receives an order for a nuke launch. Due to the circumstances of the order, the Captain refuses to fire. After escaping an attack from another U.S. sub, the crew and SEALs take refuge on a small island.

title: Copper
description: In the 1860s, an Irish-American Civil War veteran joins the New York City police force.

title: RWBY
description: Four teenage girls form Team RWBY and train to fight crime and monsters known as the Grimm, while the world of Remnant remains on the brink of an all-out war.

title: Halo 4: Forward Unto Dawn
description: UNSC Cadet Thomas Lasky must conquer his inner fears and join forces with super-soldier John-117 to take down a massive faction of the Covenant.

title: Karadayi
description: The Kara family's life is turned upside down because of a wrongful accusation that results in the imprisonment of Nazif Kara for a murder he didn't commit.

title: Hunted
description: Meet Sam. A spy. A hunter. And herself hunted by an enemy more ruthless and determined than any she's ever known.

title: The Transporter
description: Frank Martin is an ex special ops, who now spends his life as a transporter on the other side of the law. With three rules, he always completes his contracts. One way, or the other.

title: Primeval: New World
description: Canadian spin-off of Primeval (2007). A new team of scientists from the Cross Photonics company in Vancouver track down dangerous creatures emerging through anomalies in time.

title: Magi: The Labyrinth of Magic
description: Aladdin, Alibaba, and Morgiana go their separate ways after spending time together in Sindria to develop their own strengths, make new friends and prepare for what is coming.

title: Vegas
description: Ralph Lamb, a former MP for the US Army, becomes sheriff. His brother, Jack, and his son, Dixon, are deputized. Meanwhile, Vincent Savino comes from Chicago to Vegas to run The Savoy hotel and casino.

title: Miraculous anime
description: It shows how "miraculous" should have looked like in 2012, but the project was canceled and turned from anime to 3D 3 years after.

title: Aesthetica of a Rogue Hero
description: After saving a fairy-tale kingdom, Akatsuki returns to the real world with his prize--Miu, the busty daughter of the Demon King. It's one hell of a happy ending until they're force to enroll at a school for magic users.

title: Parade's End
description: Revolves around a love triangle between a conservative English aristocrat, his mean socialite wife and a young suffragette.

title: Randy Cunningham: 9th Grade Ninja
description: An ordinary ninth grader is chosen to become The Ninja. He is tasked with protecting the town from evil as well as balancing his school life with friends and homework.

title: A Touch of Cloth
description: DCI Jack Cloth and DC Anne Oldman are paired to investigate a series of grisly murders done by a devious killer.

title: Sinbad
description: A Persian prisoner sets out to find his dead brother with help from his misfit group.

title: K
description: A young boy is wanted for a crime he has no recollection of committing and must go on the run, hunted by two kings and their forces.

title: Slugterra
description: Eli Shane aims to become the greatest Slugslinging hero by collecting and dueling with transforming slug creatures to defeat the evil Dr. Blakk, who seeks to turn slugs into mindless weapons in the luminous underground world of Slugterra.

title: Metal Hurlant Chronicles
description: A look at different planets and how their inhabitants live together. The only link that connects these planets is an asteroid called the Metal Hurlant that passes close to each one of them.

title: From the New World
description: In a post-apocalyptic world set a thousand years after our era, the remaining humans, now with telekinesis, live in a seemingly peaceful society, but dark secrets of the past will soon be discovered by a small group of friends.

title: Btooom!
description: A young man gets transported into a video game he plays called Btooom. A plot is uncovered involving an organization that aims to conquer the world by dominating the virtual world.

title: Dragon Ball Absalon
description: Taking place 12 years after the battle against Omega Shenron, The Z fighters, with Goku currently absent, must defend their planet against a group of new Saiyans.

title: Wizards vs. Aliens
description: Insatiable, marauding aliens, The Nekross, invade the Earth in search of magic. Teenage schoolboy wizard Tom Clarke and his friend Benny Sherwood lead the defense against them.

title: I Miss You
description: Two middle schoolers, Soo-yeon and Jung-woo, become friends and grow close. However, an unforeseen tragedy strikes, separating them from each other. 14 years later, they are reunited as adults, but the past still lingers on their minds.

title: Flint. Redemption
description: A special squad mysteriously dies while undergoing training in the mountains, where a group of smugglers are hiding. Andrey must come out of retirement to investigate.

title: Blast of Tempest
description: Two teenage boys, Mahiro and Yoshino, try to find out more about the mysterious murder of Mahiro's sister and at the same time save the world with the help of a mage girl who's stranded on a deserted island. Together they shall have to overcome logic itself.

title: El Rostro de la Venganza
description: Diego, released 20 years after being wrongfully accused of a school massacre, is soon embroiled in a series of intrigues. With the help of the psychiatrist Antonia must uncover the mystery of the killer.

title: World War Blue
description: A parody of the console wars, the series tells the story of two nations, the Segua Kingdom and Ninteldo Empire, locked in a struggle for dominance over the land of Consume.

title: Ekip 1: Nizama Adanmis Ruhlar
description: On the one hand they try to do their job in the best way, on the other hand they have to deal with the problems in their private lives. "Orderly Devotional Spirits: Team 1", which carries the adventures of a seven-man action team on the screen, mirrors the invisible face of the policing profession.

title: Axe Cop
description: The adventures of an axe-wielding police officer dedicated to killing the various bad guys he comes across.

title: Girls und Panzer
description: Miho Nishizumi comes from a family famous for their skills in Senshado, the art of tank warfare. However, she dishonored her family name, so she attends the no-name high school called Oorai, which doesn't have a Senshado club, wanting to stay away from it. But, the student council president has other plans, wanting to save their school from termination by winning the Senshado tournament.

title: Campione!
description: Godou Kusanagi becomes a Campione, fighting Heretical Gods. His status attracts attention and complicates life, especially with forward girls like Erica Blandelli causing awkward situations.
originalTitle: Campione!: Matsurowanu Kamigami to Kamigoroshi no Maou

title: No Limit
description: A terminally ill French secret service agent is hired by Hydra, a mysterious black ops organization set up by the government, to fight crime by any means necessary and receive experimental treatment in return. Also, his daughter hates him.

title: Initial D: Fifth Stage
description: The final stage of Project D's expeditions is coming, and is to be the hardest yet.

title: Roba
description: ROBA is a 6-season Finnish television police series with Kari Hietalahti, Leena Pöysti, Riku Nieminen, Annika Aapalahti, Alex Anton, Andrei Alén, Ilari Johansson, Mari Perankoski, Rauno Ahonen and Tiina Lymi.

title: Blackout
description: A council man becomes increasingly disillusioned over the years, but a heroic act gets him approval and becomes a front-runner for the mayor-ship of Manchester while trying to keep his own secrets buried.

title: Tale of A-rang
description: Lee Eun Oh, a noble's son, arrives at a small village in search of his missing mother. There, Arang, the ghost of a young woman that lost her memories of her past life, asks him to help her to figure out her identity and how she died.

title: SheZow
description: The adventures of a boy bonded to a magic ring that turns him into a female superhero.

title: Kid Temper Tantrum
description: Get to know the family, of stressed out dad, Mom, Leland ( kid temper tantrum ), Leanna, and London. We like to do skits and make up crazy stories. *The Kid Temper Tantrum videos are acts. We post these videos for entertainment only.*

title: Batgirl: Spoiled
description: Fan-created YouTube mini-series about Batman's ally Batgirl who roams the streets of Gotham City to battle thugs and costumed super-villains.

title: Har Yug Mein Aayega Ek - Arjun
description: Arjun, rebel-cop and the lead of the Emergency Task Force, and his team solve various crime cases .He never hesitates to break the rules to ensure justice.

title: Covert Affairs: Sights Unseen
description: Details of Auggie's undercover operations are explored in this prequel to the show Covert Affairs.

title: The Ambition of Oda Nobuna
description: Suddenly finding himself in the Sengoku era, regular high school student Yoshiharu Sagara is about to be killed in the battlefield.

title: WWE Main Event
description: WWE Main Event is a professional wrestling television program produced by WWE that originally aired on Ion Television in the United States and is broadcast on the WWE Network.

title: Electric City
description: A view of the future of civilization, presented through the lens of provocative themes such as energy consumption, freedom of information, crime and punishment.

title: The Great Seer
description: The story set in the late Goryeo Dynasty in which a group of Feng Shui advisers to the government authorities help the hero Lee Sung Gye become the first king of the Joseon Dynasty.

title: Red Brazil
description: Nicolas Durand Villegaignon's expedition to Brazil in the 1550s and his struggle to create and maintain a colony, called Antarctic France, in Brazil conquered by the Portuguese.

title: Flight of the Storks
description: Jonathan Anselme (Harry Treadaway), a young English academic, teams up with Max Bohm (Danny Keogh), an amateur ornithologist, to follow storks on their migration from Switzerland to Africa. Max wants to find out why some birds never return from this journey. However, after Max is found dead in mysterious circumstances, Jonathan decides to make the trip alone, never suspecting that he will find himself caught up in an international web of intrigue. While Swiss Detective Hervé Dumaz (Clemens Schick) investigates Max Bohm's murky past, Jonathan is forced to confront his own troubled history. He uncovers a trail of grisly murders travelling through Bulgaria, Turkey, the Middle East, and the Congo, along the pathway of the migrating storks and their deadly secret.

title: Inferno Cop
description: A cop with a skeleton head towards evil around the world

title: Made in Cartagena
description: Harvey, the leader of a powerful gang, loses his son during a robbery at a major bank. When the plan fails, Flora becomes the weapon with which Harvey plots revenge. What he does not know is that love and deceit could make his plan another failure.

title: Switch
description: The adventures of a group of witches living in the city.

title: Motu Patlu
description: Motu and Patlu, two friends living in Fufuri Nagar, always get themselves into hilarious situations and later rescued merely by luck, using the help from Ghasita Ram, Inspector Chingam and Dr. Jhatka.

title: Muv-Luv Alternative: Total Eclipse
description: An alien invasion forces humanity to develop Tactical Surface Fighters for defense. Despite efforts, Eurasia is abandoned. In 2001, Japan struggles with new TSFs when a project brings pilots Yui and Yuya together, changing their destinies.

title: Misja Afganistan
description: Story about soldiers of the II platoon of the first company of the mechanized infantry from Wedrzyn, under the command of a junior officer - lieutenant Pawel Konaszewicz.

title: La Verdad: Beginnings
description: A wayward heroine in La Verdad resurfaces to help a desperate mayor fend off the rise of a new terrorist group, one year after the unexplained deaths of every single superhero on Earth.

title: Kamen Rider Wizard
description: Phantoms appear and attack the human because they create New-Phantoms from hopeless human minds. Haruto Souma uses magic rings to turn into a Kamen Rider Wizard, and fights against Phantoms. Why did he undertake his fate?

title: Bushwhacked!
description: Bushwhacked! is a high-energy, adrenalin-fueled race around Australia in search of weird, wacky and endangered species!

title: Bullet in the Face
description: A psychotic criminal tries to juggle the demands of violence and an active social life.

title: Oishi High School Battle
description: When Oishi's Dad loses his job hunting demons in outer space, and must take a crappy job on Earth working at an office supply store, Oishi must move to Earth with him, attend a regular Earth high school, and try her best to fit in.

title: Paramedicos
description: Three new paramedics face the challenge of work in the biggest city of the world, full of problems, different situations and a bunch of workmates that could make their life even worst.

title: Stupid Children
description: The adventures of 3 cousins who live in the same house for some reason.

title: La Teniente
description: A female Navy lieutenant joins Mexico's elite special operations unit after a tragedy. She must prove her worth to the male officers while dealing with the emotional challenges of her new role.

title: La storia della Arcana Famiglia
description: The patriarch of the Arcane Family, which protects the island of Regalo, must find a successor.

title: Spheres Trinity
description: Spheres Trinity is a continuation of the previous sequel, spheres unleashed / inherit the power the first indonesian tokusatsu from Surabaya Indonesia which was produce by origin pictures in the year 2006.

title: Super F***ers
description: A team of super-powered teens use their powers to get high, play pranks, and fight everyone except the bad guys.

title: The Freeman Chronicles
description: Gordon Freeman and Evan Walsh navigate the Black Mesa facility, evading the HECU soldiers led by Commander Jaegar. After a climactic confrontation, they're trapped, but the mysterious G-Man intervenes, stating Freeman's journey isn't over.

title: Robotics;Notes
description: 2019, Divergence Ratio 1.048596. The near future, where a device popularly called the PokeCom, packaged with PhoneDroid OS, spreads, bringing the Augmented Reality world close to existence. Central Tanegashima High School's Robot Research Club is in danger of losing its club status. Kaito Yashio, one of only two members, is only obsessed with robot fighting games, showing no interest in the Robo Club even in this situation. The reckless, useless club head, Akiho Senomiya, aims to complete a giant robot, struggling hard to avoid losing the club's status. Then, one day, Kaito discovers the A.R. annotation that becomes the Kimijima Report. Written in that report is the indictment of someone named Kou Kimijima's conspiracy involving the world. (Source: VNdb)

title: The Amazing Race Philippines
description: The Amazing Race Philippines is a reality television competition between eleven teams of two in a race around the Philippines. The race is divided into a number of legs wherein teams travel and complete various tasks to obtain clues to help them progress to a Pit Stop where they are given a chance to rest and recover before starting the next leg twelve hours later. The first team to arrive at a Pit Stop is often awarded a prize while the last team is normally eliminated from the race (except in non-elimination legs). The final leg of each race is run by the last three remaining teams, and the first to arrive at the final destination wins the cash prize. Hosted by Derek Ramsay.

title: Ustura Kemal
description: The story of Ustura Kemal, tired but proud of Istanbul, is reflected in the struggle for the liberation of a nation. You will be deeply impressed when you observe the stories of the people who live in the beautiful city of Istanbul and the old Istanbul, which is a songwriting subject that sheds light on the very important period of our republican history.

title: Shinobi Girl
description: As the ultra-rich and powerful claim more and more victims, Noriko fights to save one person at a time and find evidence that will prove her innocence. But Ms. Brooks, the high society trophy-wife turned widow, is hot on her trail. Her army of elite corporate assassins includes the lethal one-woman hit squad, Raven, who has her own personal agenda and score to settle! Can Noriko challenge one of the most powerful and dangerous corporations in the world and survive long enough to prove her innocence and regain her freedom? While Noriko's life precariously balances on the edge of a blade, she vows to keep up the fight for justice!

title: Air Aces
description: Ambitious, spectacular, and supercharged with thrilling action, Air Aces profiles the most harrowing airborne combat missions ever, many of which were recently declassified. Combining CGI and real-life aerial reenactments featuring actual historic aircraft, Air Aces provides a comprehensive look at these dynamic dogfights and the pilots who survived. Despite often facing insurmountable odds, the pilots profiled in this action-packed series exemplified bravery as they squared off with enemies over hot spots across the globe.

title: BeyWheelz
description: BeyWheelz is set in the futuristic city of Destection where our hero, Sho, is champion of the BeyWheelz World Tournament! This peaceful city is home to exciting and challenging battles between friends and allies until suddenly the city is attacked by an evil BeyWheelz army called the Dominators who want control over all of the BeyWheelz in the world. With the future and freedom of BeyWheelz at stake, Sho and his friends take on the Dominators' strongest fighters in an epic battle of good vs. evil.

title: La Ruta Blanca
description: THE WHITE ROUTE The lives of four strangers-- a peasant, a congresswoman, a drug lord and an actor-- intersect tragically on the harsh road of the cocaine trade.

title: Sugarless
description: The rule at Kujima High School, known as the "Windmill", is the law of the jungle. There is fierce fighting among the males who vie to reach the top. Shiba Gaku, a first year student, does nothing but spends his days fighting to get there.

title: Jeon Woo Chi
description: Jeon Woo Chi based on classical novel of unknown origin dating to the Joseon era that tells the story of a free-wheeling, mischievous Jeon Woo Chi, who swallowed the gumiho's fox bead, which gave him powers of Taoist magic. He uses those powers to save the poor, oppressed people and becomes a hero.

title: Corazones Blindados
description: The life and difficult routine of the police in Bogotá and the romantic relationship between Lieutenant Raul Avila and Deputy Lieutenant Diana Ochoa.

title: Edge
description: Juliette Edge, Chase McGovern and LeJon are secret agents and partners who go undercover to discover a mind control program.

title: Oh Sit!
description: A fun, high-stakes, high-octane musical chairs competition, in which 12 thrill-seeking daredevils race head-to-head through five physically demanding, chair-splitting obstacle course-style eliminations as they each compete to claim a chair - all to the sounds of a live band. At the end of the hour, only one contestant will be left sitting triumphant to seize the cash prize and the title of OH SIT! champion.

title: WWE Saturday Morning Slam
description: Your favorite WWE superstars in a new brand name show on saturday's.

title: Trigger Point
description: While on an undercover mission to rescue a hostage in the Pakistan-Afghanistan border area, CIA agent Tom Wisher is betrayed by Bill Blake, his corrupt handler.

title: Car-Jumper
description: A daring law-enforcement officer specializes in jumping from one car into another car.

title: A Day in the Life of Young Robin Hood
description: Ever wondered how was the daily life of Robin Hood when he was young? Challenges and situations await Young Robin of Loxley.

title: Mario Warfare
description: The Mushroom Kingdom endures Bowser's invasion. Thrilling battles blend gaming nostalgia with nods to classic films, merging humor and action.

title: Chô Soku Henkei Gyrozetter
description: In 21st century Japan, cars with artificial intelligence for increased safety, known as "A.I. cars," have revolutionized the car industry. Special schools teaching children driving A.I. cars have been established. One day, Kakeru Todoroki, a fifth grader of Arcadia Academy, was summoned by the school principal and given an A.I. car "to save the humanity by chosen drivers like you." The car, however, is not just a car but also a transforming robot known as "Gyrozetter."

title: Z.E.R.O.
description: The men and women that protect and retain zombies.

title: No Evil
description: In the land of myths and fables incarnate a group of spirits live their casual lives alongside humans, until a cataclysmic force thought to be dealt with shows once again in the world.

title: Giant Saver
description: Ten million years ago, before humans were on Earth, dragons and sea-men ruled the planet. However, the seamen and the dragons continue to fight for the map, just as the dragons have no power to fight back. The protoss from the universe have given the dragons 12 mechanical warriors and six transformation machines. Under the power of the two sides, the forces of the two sides began to balance. However, on the occasion of the heavy casualties on both sides, the Seamen discovered a more suitable water star, and began to talk with the dragons. Finally, the tyrant who ruled himself in the Haizu: the seal of the shark is sealed in the sea that controls the seawater capacity of the earth. After the door, he left the earth after a peace talk with the dragon. However, the Seamen did not know that they had invented the land-slung machine that was invented by Shark King as a gift into the Longma battleship of the Dragons, but did not know that this was actually a part of the land reorganization plan that the Shark King had created. In order to prevent the Seamen's plan, six young people with different personalities have obtained the Savers left by the dragons, and turned into warriors with three forces: Two Heaven Guards, Three Earth Guards and one Man Guard. Giant Saver, go.

title: Super Knocked Up
description: Jessica James is the most kick-ass super-villain on the planet! But... she just got knocked up. By Michael Masters. A womanizing superhero. Now Jessica must raise the baby with her nemesis! Yikes!

title: Drone
description: In the near future, war drone technology has advanced and a new weapon has been unleashed - a humanoid drone stronger and faster than any soldier. But in the aftermath of a mysterious incident, damaged battle drone 237 is forced to go on the run with its programmer (Kenneth Choi) to try and take down their corrupt commander (Lance Reddick).

title: Marina roshcha
description: Being in the epicenter of the criminal environment and closely converging with its inhabitants, Troshin unravels cold-blooded murders, daring raids and ingenious scams. He sets himself the task of eradicating the crime itself.

title: Vigilante Project
description: When his kid sister is kidnapped, raped, and murdered, an apathetic college student finds purpose in tracking down the man responsible, and risks everything to save another little girl being held by the same man.

title: Witness Insecurity
description: What will a man do when torn between love and duty? Hui Wai Sam (Bosco Wong) is an officer in the Witness Protection Unit (WPU). He is assigned to protect Kiu Chi Lam (Linda Chung), a cellist who is the daughter of wealthy businessman Kiu Kong San (Paul Chun), after she witnesses the attempted killing of her father's brother. Chi Lam has already been living with a tremendous amount of guilt over the death of her brother at a young age, but through Wai Sam, she begins to feel happiness again. Despite Kong San's opposition, Chi Lam and Wai Sam begin a romantic relationship.

title: Kyousou Giga
description: Five tales about different characters from the world of Kyosogiga. Three kids are stuck in a strange city causing massive mayhem through the land. They are searching for an atypical rabbit in order to return home. Koto, the eldest of the three, seems to have some sort of connection to this weird place ruled by a monk, a demon, and a priest.

title: GCPD: Major Crimes Unit
description: Jim Gordon III is a prodigy detective and expert marksman from a bloodline of justice. He is Commissioner Gordon's grandson, Barbara "Batgirl" Gordon's son, and Gotham City's last and only hope for survival.

title: Territory Cops
description: A look into the daily life of the police in the Northern Territory.

title: Synarchy
description: In his lifetime Stefano Terenzio had a merciless ambition for absolute power. A generation later, what started with one man's ego will determine the fate of the whole word. For centuries a secret organization that has been controlling world governments and religion since the dawn of man, known as The Roshaniya. They have lied, sacrificed man by the thousands, and manipulated humanity into their service and they will stop at nothing to keep their control of planet Earth. The new head of the Terenzio family Vasco and his siblings, Simone and Lucien plan to take down an unbeatable enemy in this action packed series to free Earth from it's chains and give humanity a choice it's never been given before.

title: Busou Shinki
description: High school freshman Rihito, who just came back from abroad, started a new life in Japan with his four Busou Shinki, female action figures with weapons.

title: Minecraft Multiplayer Challenges
description: Various members of the Yogscast family participate in competitive Co-op and PVP games such as Race for the Wool and Survival Games. Who will win?

title: The Hunter's Moon
description: A new series by Terminal 52 Films, this prequel to "The Hunter's Saga" tells the story of Jacob Chapel Sr. and Victoria Rayne, the parents of Joseph and Jacob Chapel. Jacob Chapel Sr. is one of the founders of the 8 Sides of the Black Lotus. Victoria Chapel one of the high-ranking hunters of The Society. See how their love grew, how they helped shape the Society, how Jade rose to power, and how the 8 Sides of the Black Lotus came into power. Plus, see many back stories on various characters in the Hunter's Saga and how some of the characters might have encountered one another sooner than you thought.

title: Raw Heat
description: Detectives John McHeat and Douglas Rawthorne face off against the corrupt political machine headed by Mayor Barnabie and his thugs.

title: Midnight Frights
description: "Midnight Frights" was a hosted horror movie show with Armistead Wellford as "Armistead Spottswoode", presenting movies on the OSI 74 Roku Channel; from 2012.

title: The Creepy Guy
description: The Creepy Guy is a short film shot in a park in North Los Angeles; it depicts how hard it is to approach women when a man has social inadequacies, and also how hard the single scene is. Ben/the creepy guy has a friendly disposition and is well known in this park; he is a nice person but has little social skills and major boundary problems. The moral of this story is that women who dump nice guys for muscular men can get hurt, because these men can be players, like in the case of Troy. Also, if you are a man who goes around approaching women in creepy ways, do not do that anymore.

title: Viento Sur
description: Stories that marked the life of Patagonia in 30s and 40s. The society was a interplay of culture of indigenous peoples with the Welsh immigrants, Italian, Spanish and Lebanese, will enliven facts and circumstances that speak of those times.

title: The Brothers Russell
description: Two brothers engage in a series of friendly and not-so-friendly competitions to see which sibling will come out on top.

title: Strelok
description: Andrei Makarov is back. He will have to expose the conspiracy of foreign intelligence services, bring to light the big corrupt officials and save their loved ones. This time he will be helped by a young intelligence officer Yegor Bodrov. It was Egor's father who was a comrade and mentor of Strelka on his first "real" mission in the Caucasus mountains. Makarov and Bodrov will have to enter into an unequal battle with dangerous militants - and do everything possible to win ...

title: Toxic Tales AKA Toxic Tales with Timber Wulff
description: "Toxic Tales with Timber Wulff" is a hosted horror / science fiction movie show with Ken Halhober as "Timber Wulff".

title: Vigilante
description: When the city of Los Angeles is taken over by a maniacal brute with the law on his side-one man stands up to them. An unknown man whose bravery will be tested. All in the hopes of inspiring bravery in others.

title: Dead Man's Trigger
description: Two FBI agents race against the clock to stop a bomb from destroying New York City.

title: Final Fantasy VII: The Sacrifice of Cloud
description: Just as Sephiroth is about to kill her, Cloud pushes her out of the way.

title: Medal of Honor: History of Heroes
description: On December 21, 1861 President Abraham Lincoln approved and signed Senate Bill 82 into law, creating the Medal Of Honor for heroic acts above and beyond the call of duty, for gallantry in the face of enemy forces engaged in combat.

title: Nuea mek song: Mue prap chom khamang wet
Survival of the Dumbest
description: Three half witted friends fight to survive in the wake of a zombie apocalypse. They attempt to stay among the living despite all the chaos around them.

title: Voyna v Koree
description: Star Media's award-winning animation studio, Babich Design proudly presents this powerful and dramatic account of the Korean War (1950-1953). Often colloquially referred to as 'The Forgotten War', it was nevertheless one of the most dangerous big-power confrontations and threats to world peace since World War 2 with a bitter legacy of hatred and suspicion enduring to the present day. With a combination of stunning CGI animation, dramatic reconstruction and unique historic library footage, the full and harrowing details of this brutal and bloody war are vividly recreated for today's television audience for many of whom the war is a distant memory or a mere item in the history books.

title: Yok Luerd Mungkorn
description: Jao Sua Leng, the 2nd generation dragon heir to Mongkorn Waree. He arranged for a celebration to introduce his project that cost more than a billion without listening to the objection from his left hand, Lao Ngow, a close friend of his dad who helped build his family's fortune. Lao Ngow was jealous and wanted to get rid of Jao Sua Leng by sending Duangkae to be Jao Sua's lover so she can spy for him. During the banquet a group of hitmen invaded and shot many people there dead including Jao Sua's wife and his kid (s). Jao Sua narrowly escaped death with the help of Praosaeng, a waitress there. She took care of him and the two felt in love resulting in her pregnancy. The hitmen caught up with the two, in fear of his wife and child's safety Jao Sua arranged for them to escape before him. He bestowed upon his unborn child a red dragon jade, the family treasure and vowed to come back to get them after he deal with the bad guys. But Praosaeng wasn't able to escape the hitmen who came after her. Jao Sua was able to escape death this time because of Duangkae, his mistress. Lao Ngow was served with the allegation of trying to assassinate Jao Sua and was sentenced to life in prison. Daungkae backstabbed Lao Ngow because she wanted Manop, her 5 years old son with him to become the heir Jao Sua's fortune despite the fact that Manop is not Jao Sua's real son. Twenty years later, Yok, a young man with a bright future will soon graduate from the Royal Police Cadet Academy despite being an orphan and living in the slum. He was raised by an ex-boxer who now opened a school that teaches boxing to young kids. He told Yok that he discovered Yok's mother who was injured and decided to help her. He was able to save her until she passed away after giving birth to Yok. She refused to tell him the father of the baby, with only the red dragon jade by her side he named the baby, Yok.

title: A.Z.A.S: All Zombies Are Stupid
description: Carson City, 2012. Robin D'Amico and Frank Enselmo are great friends. They are two young guys fans of horror movies and horror videogames. Their dream? A ZOMBIE INVASION! Docky is a very wacky doctor, he's their best friend. Docky discovers the T-ICK VIRUS, a virus that can give life to the dead. The Mayor Fossi discovers the virus and he will order his henchmen to take the Virus and scatter it in the country. Why? Because the mayor wants create the Zombie Park, an amusement park with the living dead. This two young, funny and bumbling boys, are they ready to face this new adventure? What do they have to do to survive? They will have to ESCAPE FROM THE COUNTRY! Violence, profanity, shootings, quotes and many many laughs await you.

description: Extreme Vacations is a luxury adventure travel show that brings you to some of the most fascinating destinations on the planet. Told through eyes of host Pam Glennon, the half hour documentary travel series brings you on an informational and personal journey to understand the stories, cultures, and excitement of places people only dream of vacationing at. See spectacular accommodations and resorts, view incredible sites, and take a walk on the dangerous side as we take on some of the most thrilling and exhilarating activities known to man.

description: Derek comes back to the neighborhood he grew up in and hates. The projects are giving way to Whole Foods, the rents are insane and kids are fighting in dungeons with swords and axes. Wait, swords and axes?

description: In this 6 part film, Roberto Etchegaray, a soon to be retired police officer, has to investigate the murder of his best friend and partner. But when he finally discover the truth, he wishes he never knew it.

title: Splinter Cell: Operation Phoenix
description: It is 1983 and twenty-years before the formation of "Third Echelon," a young Naval Graduate named Sam Fisher, is stationed in West Germany. It is there that he assists with a raid on a suspected drug-trafficking ring, operated by the notorious Manuel Noriega. After the operation goes awry, the CIA takes note of Fisher's ability to successfully disrupt the shipment and extract information regarding the pipeline's destination, without any reinforcements. Fisher is approached by the CIA and assigned to the "Special Activities Division," where he will spend the next few years uncovering Noriega's whereabouts and eliminate the drug-trafficking ring. Operation Phoenix is a non-profit fan-series intended to celebrate the "Splinter Cell" franchise and is in no way affiliated with Tom Clancy or Ubisoft.

title: Sigo Vivo
description: Ahora que llega el verano todo el mundo quiere ir de vacaciones parece que 2 amigos Foster y Aliri an decidido ir a un lugar llamado Evocity situado al Oeste del Estado de Flagtrass y Construct al parecer sus vacaciones se han doblado un poco y no han salido como planeaban dando lugar a un gran acontecimiento en el que tendrá lugar un virus que desata el canibalismo entre todos los habitantes de Evocity conseguirán salir de la ciudad y evitar esta catastrófica desdicha...

description: An Enforcer returns to Earth in the body of Jake's deceased fiancée to ask for his help in stopping the rogue agent of Death who killed her before her time.

title: Genoma
description: Adán is happy with his life: he has a wonderful girlfriend, Emma, and a good job. But all of that is going to change sooner than he thinks...

title: Heroics 101
description: Follow the adventures of warriors, maidens and sorcerer's as they journey across the mystical land of Ashur trying to learn what it truly means to be a "HERO" battling armies of bandits, warlords, monsters and sometimes...grandmothers pie. Join us in a world where magic is rampant and where heroes stand true.

title: Hong Sabat Lai
description: Nay witnessed the murder of her parents at a very young age. She was carted off to Paris to be raised by her father's best friend-a businessman-while her younger brother Vee was taken under their driver's wing, living a humble life as his son in Thailand. Fast-forward ten years and Nay has grown up a regal and beautiful woman. She's engaged to Siwat-her father's best friend's son-however, they cannot marry until they fulfil their ultimate goal to avenge her parent's murder. In order to return to Thailand to execute their plan and remain safe from the bad guys, they hire a bodyguard, Rabin, to protect Nay.
